description: Provides information about the runs of a journey.

parameters.name: ApplicationId
parameters.description: The unique identifier for the application. This identifier is displayed as the Project ID on the Amazon Pinpoint console.

parameters.name: JourneyId
parameters.description: The unique identifier for the journey.

nested_items.name: JourneyRunsResponse
nested_items.description: Provides information from all runs of a journey.

nested_items.name: Item
nested_items.description: An array of responses, one for each run of the journey.

nested_items.name: CreationTime
nested_items.description: The time when the journey run was created or scheduled, in ISO 8601 format.

nested_items.name: LastUpdateTime
nested_items.description: The last time the journey run was updated, in ISO 8601 format..

nested_items.name: RunId
nested_items.description: The unique identifier for the run.

nested_items.name: Status
nested_items.description: The current status of the journey run.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: The string to use in a subsequent request to get the next page of results in a paginated response. This value is null if there are no additional pages.
